"{\"uid\": \"bostonherald.com-2024-01-12-ticker-us-intensifies-oversight-of-boeing-olympics-brings-on-its-first-beer-brand-as-a-global-sponsor\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"E-Edition  Sign up for email newsletters    Sign up for email newsletters  E-Edition  Trending:  The Federal Aviation Administration says it will increase oversight of Boeing and audit production of the 737 Max 9 jetliner after a panel blew off an Alaska Airlines plane in midflight last week, the latest in a string of mishaps at the\\u00a0troubled aircraft maker.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 101, \"end\": 132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Federal Aviation Administration\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\"}, {\"begin\": 248, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alaska Airlines\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alaska_Airlines\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The FAA said Friday that it would judge whether Boeing and its suppliers followed approved quality procedures.\", \"from\": 361, \"to\": 471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2418458368949994e-22, \"text\": \"FAA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The FAA also said it's reconsidering a longstanding practice of relying on employees at aircraft manufacturers to perform some safety analysis of planes.\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 626, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 477, \"end\": 480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2418458368949994e-22, \"text\": \"FAA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Aviation_Administration\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Members of Congress criticized the practice of deputizing Boeing employees as inspectors after two deadly crashes involving Boeing 737 Max 8 planes in 2018 and 2019.\", \"from\": 627, \"to\": 792, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 638, \"end\": 646, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"score\": 0.9999999581743859, \"rank\": 3.57060978335348e-08, \"text\": \"Congress\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Congress\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_737_MAX\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boeing 737 Max 8\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_737_MAX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_737_MAX\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 767, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_737_MAX\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Boeing 737 Max 8\", \"types\": [\"Q11436\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_737_MAX\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boeing_737_MAX\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The International Olympic Committee has signed Anheuser-Busch InBev as the first beer brand in the 40-year history of its sponsorship program, which earns billions of dollars for the organization and international sports.\", \"from\": 794, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 798, \"end\